description:
Cube Airport is a puzzle game where your objective is to construct a runway to enable the airplane to take off safely. To do this, you need to correctly fit the runway cubes into the indicated positions on the platform and proceed to the next level.

Features:
- 40 levels;
- Original soundtrack;
- Satisfactory puzzles;
- Low poly;

Developer Colossus Game Studio 
Publisher GramikGames
